PGZ0W3XDnkU.title: Eating Street Food in Philippines Chinatown and Trying Filipino KFC
PGZ0W3XDnkU.description:
Today we visit the oldest Chinatown in the world... and it's in Manila!

Our tour guide (Kelbing) takes us around the Philippines to try street food from wonderful vendors. We also try yum cha and traditional Filipino foods along the way.
Join us as we explore the Philippines for the first time!

__________________________________________________________________

It's our first time visiting Gwangjang Market. We watched the Netflix series 'Street Food' which featured a few food stalls from Gwangjang market and had to try them out.

We also stayed at a Hanok (traditional Korean house) and tried the new menu from McDonald's in Korea. It was a big fat food day!

PzVypF3vfYo.title: Staying at a Shin Ramyun Noodle Home
PzVypF3vfYo.description:

A very interesting place to visit. Although, it is in the middle of no where and there aren't any restaurants or transportation close by. Research before you go!

cQ7cDbfuPdY.title: CHONNY GOES ON A 10 DAY DIET
cQ7cDbfuPdY.description:
Hey guys! For the the past 10 days, I've been on a intense diet and exercise plan. It has been deadly but very rewarding!

I've gained a bit of weight over the year/s and have wanted to get fit again. AND THE TIMING IS NOW!!!
It's definitely a lot harder to lose weight at my age (my metabolism is a lot slower than it used to be) but I had to soldier on and fight my way through haha
Vlogging the experience was very motivating and kept me on my dietary plan. I plan on continuing with my diet/exercise and will keep you guys updated on a regular basis! Let's hope I don't gain all the weight back.
ALL the food you see in this video is what I ate. I didn't sneak in a hamburger or any snacks... COLD TURKEY DAT BISH!

If you enjoyed the vlog, please give it a LIKE and SUBSCRIBE!
I'll have a regular, FUN vlog for you guys next week but will continue to film my workout/diets (trying intermittent fasting for 10 days)

Follow me on:
Instagram: @lechonny 
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/mychonny
Comedy Channel: http://www.youtube.com/yourchonny
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Mychonny-146853695356556/

THANKS FOR WATCHING!
